== Overview ==
The multi-launch Light Rocket pack is able to cause reasonable damage to multiple targets by firing of a salvo of rockets that rain down over a small area.

== Where to Acquire ==
The LR100 Rocket Pack can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.
